WEBVTT

00:00:03.280 --> 00:00:13.439
Well, praise the Lord. Let me know when some people are showing up.

00:00:13.440 --> 00:01:03.679
I don't see it yet. Can you hear us? Yeah. Can you hear us? Is it loud and clear?

00:01:03.680 --> 00:01:15.209
Yep. They can hear us. Well, good evening, family. I won't say good morning today. Well, it's morning always somewhere.

00:01:15.210 --> 00:01:27.688
People say, "Why do you always say morning, Brandon?"I say, "Well, because it's morning somewhere, but good evening here in America. I feel in my heart we have much prayer to do.

00:01:27.689 --> 00:01:41.279
That's why I keep doing these lives."You know, yesterday we did the live broadcast and we had 6,700 people praying with us at a time altogether within that time span.

00:01:41.280 --> 00:01:48.522
Braden said, "Dad, we had over 50,000 people praying."And so we give all the glory to God for that.

00:01:48.523 --> 00:01:59.340
That all 50,000 of you at one point of that hour and a half, two hours, whatever it was, were praying for Charlie and his family and for our beautiful nation.

00:01:59.341 --> 00:02:05.949
So 50,000 people is a lot and I believe that many hands make light work.

00:02:05.950 --> 00:02:45.833
So my heart tonight is to come and pray as a family again for the capture of this man that did this heinous act, that we would help aid and assist in prayer the FBI, Homeland Security, and that there would be no rock, no cave, no cabin, no hotel room, nor any place at all that would be able to harbor this man, that he would be exposed and brought to justice swiftly, that this would not be a long drawn out process, that this would be a quick work.

00:02:45.834 --> 00:02:51.171
And so I already feel in my heart it's been too long. He needs to be brought to justice.

00:02:51.172 --> 00:03:02.467
But what we know in the spirit, as I have been praying over this all day today, is there's more than one.

00:03:02.468 --> 00:03:14.227
I know there was one shooter, but there is more than one person that has accompanied this man and that is involved with this.

00:03:14.228 --> 00:03:20.479
This is a lot deeper of a rabbit hole than what people realize.

00:03:20.480 --> 00:03:58.559
And so I was visited—and I'll say this carefully—I was visited by the Lord prophetically last night very late and He gave me the layout of a big scheme of things and He told me, "I will not allow you to put this on a public platform,"what He has told me of a deeper, darker plan that is much more involved than what anyone could ever realize.

00:03:58.560 --> 00:04:19.757
And so whenever He was giving me so much detail, it was alarming, but at the same time, when you flow with the Spirit of the Lord, I just can't comprehend that kind of evil because His word is not evil.

00:04:19.757 --> 00:04:32.392
But when you see that people are demonically energized, you know, the Bible says we wrestle not against flesh and blood, but we wrestle against principalities and powers and spirits of wickedness in high places.

00:04:32.393 --> 00:04:40.879
We wrestle against demonic spirits. The principalities are working through personalities.

00:04:40.880 --> 00:04:49.457
So the people are just yielded vessels to a demonic spirit in any area.

00:04:49.457 --> 00:04:52.799
The devil will work through a personality, will work through a person.

00:04:52.800 --> 00:05:14.959
So that's what we're praying for tonight, to pray for confusion in the enemy's camp, that the plots and the plans of the wicked will be uncovered and the innocent lives will be spared.

00:05:14.960 --> 00:05:24.686
The innocent lives will be spared. We have a job to do. And that's why the Lord, I believe with all my heart, has raised us up for such a time as this.

00:05:24.687 --> 00:05:42.968
If you go back to one of my very first dreams that I had concerning YouTube, I was walking out of this building and it was a school cafeteria, and the Lord said, "I've called you to go in there and teach the children.

00:05:42.969 --> 00:05:54.920
I want you to teach them how to pray."And out of disobedience, I walked out and I said, "I don't want to do this assignment."And a whirlwind whipped me around and put me back at the school building.

00:05:54.921 --> 00:06:08.125
And He said, "Go teach My people to pray."And I said, "Yes, Lord."So I opened the door and I went in and there was a school auditorium and it was full of children that needed to learn how to pray.

00:06:08.126 --> 00:06:18.530
And He said, "Teach My people to pray. Go and pray."So I took that assignment and that's what we've been doing.

00:06:18.531 --> 00:06:35.076
I saw the sky was split in half and the moon was turning into darkness and I could hear the air raid sirens blowing all around and I knew there was a storm coming. I knew there was a storm coming.

00:06:35.077 --> 00:06:53.994
And the purpose of this channel, for this YouTube broadcast, is always to bring glory to God, to deflect always to Him, to always let you know that Brandon Biggs is just a vessel that is used by the Father and that anybody can do it.

00:06:53.995 --> 00:07:00.799
Anybody can pray. I want you to know that He'll use you right where you are if you just say yes.

00:07:00.800 --> 00:07:08.409
And so the other part is to pray for us to change things as we see the days approaching.

00:07:08.410 --> 00:07:16.438
It's getting darker and darker, and Diana and I, we're so excited that you all would show up on a daily basis.

00:07:16.439 --> 00:07:25.771
And I'm not here to ramble, but I want you to be very serious and really engaged tonight. We have work to do.

00:07:25.772 --> 00:08:03.089
We saw through his sister in an email that when I told you all about Alabama—and I saw Alabama, you know, when you're talking in front of thousands of people, I try not to be, as I told Di, I said, "I'm more bold whenever I'm just talking to us and I'm making a video versus a live feed."But when I saw Alabama and I saw the Crimson and I said, "There's a planned mass event at this place,"and I saw Texas and I saw college campuses, to pray for college football games and tailgate parties.

00:08:03.090 --> 00:08:11.589
Then an article comes out today saying that there were threats made at these places.

00:08:11.590 --> 00:08:18.351
So we know we're on the right trail. We're hearing the news before the news has the news.

00:08:18.351 --> 00:08:37.918
And that's why we know we're on target praying for protection over our young people at the college campuses and at the tailgate parties because the Lord told me, He said, "Brandon, there'll be a great move of My Spirit, a great revival on college campuses around the United States.

00:08:37.919 --> 00:08:48.260
It will not just be—it'll be like popcorn."That's whenever you take a pan of coconut oil and the popcorn seeds and you heat it up.

00:08:48.261 --> 00:09:04.968
You don't know which popcorn's going to pop first, but you just know in anticipation that the more you heat it up, the more the heat comes on those corn kernels, it's going to start to have a reaction and the popcorn's coming.

00:09:04.969 --> 00:09:08.993
So we know that what the Spirit of the Lord has warned us, He does.

00:09:08.994 --> 00:09:25.999
He told us, He said, "I'm going to do something unusual with My college campuses around the United States of America."Specifically, there will be a major move of God, a major harvest of souls with the young people.

00:09:26.000 --> 00:09:33.272
And it would start with the young people. You'll start to see a major glory in the college campuses.

00:09:33.273 --> 00:09:49.310
So I'm believing even tonight that if you have young people at a college campus, that the fire starts with them, that they'll be spiritual—I'm not saying physical, but spiritual—arsonists, that they would set the fire.

00:09:49.311 --> 00:10:13.893
Like William Seymour: "Dip me in the kerosene of Thy Spirit, set my heart ablaze that I may burn for You."I know that there has to be—there's that point in time where we're going to see that wave, the beginning of the fruit of this major revival throughout America and around the world.

00:10:13.894 --> 00:10:25.199
I know there's places that are seeing things, but we have not seen very much yet in America. And I believe that there's a great shaking to awaken.

00:10:25.200 --> 00:10:43.372
And from what I saw last night, I would love to be able to tell maybe the authorities, like the Secret Service or whatever, for the detail that I saw concerning an attack against America and in certain places.

00:10:43.373 --> 00:10:51.999
I saw more about the ten cities, great detail about the ten cities last night.

00:10:52.000 --> 00:11:03.278
And this was very heavy and I prayed and interceded for this for a long time. And so that's what we're going to pray over tonight.

00:11:03.279 --> 00:11:12.952
But our main priority is to pray for this man and all the people who helped him to be brought to justice quickly.

00:11:12.953 --> 00:11:19.340
Okay. So y'all want to go tubing? I'm not going to—I don't have anything else other than that. I've dumped out for the last several days.

00:11:19.341 --> 00:11:33.074
And I told Diana, I go, 'I've got to get refreshed, but at the same time, I feel an urgency to pray.'So, how many people are here?

00:11:33.075 --> 00:11:37.474
2,600. Okay. You can take communion. We're going to take communion.

00:11:37.475 --> 00:11:47.359
I never go into the river until I take communion first. You know me, I always make sure I cover all my bases.

00:11:47.360 --> 00:11:54.057
And so, Father, we just lift up the body before you. We thank you, Lord, that you were wounded for our transgressions.

00:11:54.058 --> 00:12:01.919
You were bruised for our iniquities. The chastisement of our peace was upon you, and with your stripes, we are healed.

00:12:01.920 --> 00:12:08.045
And we believe we receive everything that you have for us. We will lack no good thing, Lord.

00:12:08.046 --> 00:12:16.207
And we are healed in our flesh, in our minds, in our bodies, everything. We're made whole because of this body.

00:12:16.208 --> 00:12:27.453
You took it all on the cross for us to walk in victory over every area of our life—mentally, physically, financially, all of it.

00:12:27.454 --> 00:12:37.315
You took it for us to have an abundant life. And I believe, Father, that I receive that abundant life right now by faith, that I will lack nothing.

00:12:37.316 --> 00:12:41.695
I will lack no good thing. I will walk in the abundant believing.

00:12:41.696 --> 00:12:45.833
I'm a believing believer who walks in the abundance in Jesus'name.

00:12:45.834 --> 00:12:52.396
And we take this body, and we thank you, Lord, that you died for us and you rose again on that third day.

00:12:52.397 --> 00:12:58.127
And Father, I thank you that you're making intercession for us and you're seated at the right hand of the Father.

00:12:58.128 --> 00:13:03.912
I give you all the glory, honor, and praise. Father, we take this body in Jesus'name.

00:13:03.913 --> 00:13:11.995
Amen. Now, Lord, we thank you for the blood. And I plead the blood of Jesus all around my house.

