I plead the blood of Jesus all around my car, my finances, over my children, over my wife, over even our dogs.

00:13:21.968 --> 00:13:31.838
I plead the blood of Jesus over us, Father, for it never loses its power. And we make much of the blood, and the blood makes much of us.

00:13:31.839 --> 00:13:39.293
You said a thousand shall fall at our side and 10,000 at our right hand, but nothing shall come nigh us.

00:13:39.294 --> 00:13:44.894
