00:13:44.895 --> 00:13:52.932
Every word, every spell, every incantation, every chant, every voodoo, anything that tries to come against us in the spiritual realm falls to our feet.

00:13:52.933 --> 00:14:00.496
It does not bear fruit of any kind in the name of Jesus. We plead the blood of Jesus against it.

00:14:00.497 --> 00:14:05.994
And we thank you, Lord. I thank you, Lord, that whom God has blessed, no man can curse.

00:14:05.995 --> 00:14:13.109
I thank you for the blessing. The blessing and the favor of God follows me all the days.

00:14:13.110 --> 00:14:19.723
For goodness and mercy follow me all the days of my life, and I'll dwell in the house of the Lord forever.

00:14:19.724 --> 00:14:25.811
I thank you, Lord, for that blood. I thank you, Lord, that we make much of that blood tonight. We plead the blood of Jesus.

00:14:25.812 --> 00:14:35.994
We thank you, Lord, for angels and aid and assistance all around this house, all around us, that your angels are bearing us up in their hands lest we dash our foot against a stone.

00:14:35.995 --> 00:14:39.516
We thank you, Lord, for the blood. We thank you, Lord, for your covenant.

00:14:39.517 --> 00:14:46.461
We thank you, Lord, that we have much favor because of you, Lord, and we give you, Father, all the glory, honor, and praise.

00:14:46.462 --> 00:15:01.152
For you said, 'If I be lifted up, I'll draw all men unto you.'And I thank you, Father, in the name of Jesus, for that anointing, burden-removing, yoke-destroying power that flows on the inside of us in the mighty name of Jesus.

00:15:01.153 --> 00:15:08.636
Amen and amen. You take the blood. You say, 'Well, that's different.'Yep, that is.

00:15:08.637 --> 00:15:19.359
I take it in the way the Lord tells me to. So, I've just been reading over Ephesians.

00:15:19.360 --> 00:15:36.638
You really—I'm going to say this: in all the times of being serious about your covenant, serious about who you are in Christ, this is more of an alert time than ever before.

00:15:36.639 --> 00:15:47.119
This is a time like never before that you are awake and don't have a spiritual slumber about you.

00:15:47.120 --> 00:15:52.653
It's time for you to arise and shine, for the light has come and the glory of the Lord is risen upon you.

00:15:52.654 --> 00:16:03.270
It's time for you to be the salt in this earth like never before, wherever you are, being that voice similar to Charlie.

00:16:03.271 --> 00:16:13.039
We've watched a lot of his videos—Diana did today—of everything that that man said and what he stood for, and, man, it blesses.

00:16:13.040 --> 00:16:30.624
She said, 'Man, it challenges me when you see somebody who stood and died for the cause of Christ like a martyr, and you see what they meant to so many people and the impartation of wisdom that he had.'It was Holy Ghost-given.

00:16:30.625 --> 00:16:39.350
I'm telling you, that's not normal to be that witty. You know when the spirit of God is on somebody.

00:16:39.351 --> 00:16:47.758
And there are so many people criticizing in emails and things, saying, 'Brandon, you see so much. Why didn't you see this?

00:16:47.759 --> 00:17:00.019
If you truly have a gift and God shows you things, how come you didn't see this?'And I can only tell you that I only see in part, and I hear in part, and it's as the Spirit wills.

00:17:00.020 --> 00:17:05.979
I don't have control over it. And He shows me what I'm supposed to see for that day.

00:17:05.980 --> 00:17:14.899
And obviously, He did not see that I needed to see that. I'm not God. And I am telling you this: I am far from anything cool.

00:17:14.900 --> 00:17:21.838
I'm going to tell you, I'm only filled with and controlled by the Holy Ghost, like I pray you all are.

00:17:21.839 --> 00:17:28.798
And as I develop and I see things, I try to wrap my mind around it.

00:17:28.799 --> 00:17:31.622
I ask the Lord all the time, 'Lord, we could have been praying for him more.

00:17:31.623 --> 00:17:39.317
We could...'You take it personally. Lord, help us. I don't want to see a brother in the Lord die like that.

00:17:39.318 --> 00:17:49.588
I don't want to see anybody have a tragic event like that. But all I can tell you is that we live in a fallen world and sometimes things happen.

00:17:49.589 --> 00:18:25.439
And at the same time, it's like when people try to say to us, 'How come you didn't see Megan getting that shot and all that happened to her?'I said, 'That morning when I went to the doctor's office and they gave it to her, I heard the Spirit of the Lord yelling, "Do not do it!"But I disobeyed out of fear of that virus versus trusting that God was telling me not to do something.'I don't know where He was.

00:18:25.440 --> 00:18:31.519
