00:18:41.039 --> 00:18:46.206
We don't go, 'Well, God did this, He did that.'No, I don't believe God's a kill, steal, and destroy God.

00:18:46.207 --> 00:18:55.999
Regardless of what we go through and how hard things seem to be sometimes, God is a good God and the devil is a bad devil.

00:18:56.000 --> 00:19:01.175
So, there's a lot of people asking, 'Brandon, why? Why? Why?'I don't know why.

00:19:01.176 --> 00:19:05.484
I don't know why. And that's a good enough answer. I don't know why.

00:19:05.485 --> 00:19:15.069
I don't have a clue, to be real with you. But all I know is that God is a good God and the devil's a bad devil. And that's where I stay.

00:19:15.070 --> 00:19:23.114
