02:07:40.681 --> 02:07:47.198
You may not be polished and speaking like he was, but you have something that he doesn't have.

02:07:47.199 --> 02:07:52.996
Do you understand? You are special in your own right. You have your own special gift inside of you.

02:07:52.997 --> 02:07:58.879
And you've just got to polish it up and figure out what God's called you to do.

02:07:58.880 --> 02:08:06.694
You may be the best pie maker, the best cookie maker, or whatever it is.

02:08:06.695 --> 02:08:11.113
And you could fund the gospel by selling your pies or selling your cookies.

02:08:11.114 --> 02:08:16.703
It may not be speaking, is what I'm trying to say. Not everybody's called to speak behind a pulpit.

02:08:16.704 --> 02:08:25.678
Not everybody is, but somebody's called to maybe bake a cake and sell it, and support the gospel and support the preacher behind the camera.

02:08:25.679 --> 02:08:30.822
Do you understand? Not everybody's going to be called to have a platform and talk on YouTube.

02:08:30.823 --> 02:08:35.137
Not everybody is. But somebody might be good at car washing.

02:08:35.138 --> 02:08:44.566
Somebody might be good at filing taxes, or being an auditor, or whatever. I don't know, I'm just saying.

02:08:44.567 --> 02:08:53.598
Somebody might be good at something, and you're called to help out with that area.

02:08:53.599 --> 02:09:00.158
Whatever you do, in word and in deed, do all to the glory of God.

02:09:00.159 --> 02:09:10.551
All that you do. Say, "God, I'm sold out. I'm the best yard guy. I'm the best pool cleaner.

02:09:10.552 --> 02:09:21.198
I could be flipping burgers at McDonald's, but I'm the best burger flipper in all of this whole area, and everybody's going to see me and see that there's glory on me.

02:09:21.199 --> 02:09:34.757
And I might not be flipping burgers that much; I might be owning the restaurant soon and have a chain of burger joints."I don't know, but whatever you do, do all to the glory of God.

02:09:34.758 --> 02:09:44.729
And I believe God will promote you, and you won't just be like I was for so long—a janitor for 14 or 15 years.

02:09:44.730 --> 02:09:51.972
God can do something big in your life if you just say, "Yes, Lord. Here am I."That's what I'm trying to tell you.

02:09:51.973 --> 02:09:58.906
No matter what you're doing, be the best ditch digger in all of the county so they go, "Man, you're good at digging ditches.

02:09:58.907 --> 02:10:01.979
We need more of you."You might say, "I don't like this,"but you know what?

02:10:01.980 --> 02:10:09.279
Do it all to the glory of God. So, I don't know, that's what I had.

02:10:09.280 --> 02:10:20.399
How many people are here? 51. Still quite a few. Do you have any questions at all?

02:10:20.400 --> 02:10:30.976
I can end it there. I know we've been on here quite a while. So, thank you, Lord, that they're bringing that man to justice.

02:10:30.977 --> 02:10:41.955
Thank you, Lord. Hallelujah. Do you like our new background tonight? Is that pretty cool? I changed it.

02:10:41.956 --> 02:10:53.564
I had Braden change it from the tent to a major coliseum full of people worshiping Jesus. I thought it was kind of neat.

02:10:53.565 --> 02:11:03.415
I told him, I said, "Make it full of people, and they're all there for a revival."I thought it was kind of cool.

02:11:03.416 --> 02:11:06.799
I got tired of the tent. I said, "Let's do something different other than the tent.

02:11:06.800 --> 02:11:20.715
Let's do it inside."Something more that looked like there are more people there than the tent revival, because I'm telling you, that looks like a Dallas Cowboys stadium or something.

02:11:20.716 --> 02:11:28.968
That's a huge stadium. Well, we love you all. Could you do us a favor?

02:11:28.969 --> 02:11:35.067
We never ask you to do anything. We never do, but this is the only thing we will ask you to do.

02:11:35.068 --> 02:11:43.937
So, if anybody asks you in the comment section, saying we're trying to get you to give us money or invest or anything, we're here to give out, not to take from you.

02:11:43.938 --> 02:11:49.232
Listen, we want you to subscribe by clicking the like button.

02:11:49.233 --> 02:11:53.874
Click the subscribe button. It's free, please. It's free. All we're asking you to do is subscribe.

02:11:53.875 --> 02:11:57.026
We're not here to sell you anything. We're not here to do anything.

02:11:57.027 --> 02:12:01.136
We're here just to tell you Jesus loves you, and we're praying for you.

02:12:01.137 --> 02:12:13.742
And so, if you could just subscribe, if you could like, if you could comment something nice down below—not on this, but on the other thread, because this thread is fixing to go away, and we have this new one that is fixing to go.

02:12:13.743 --> 02:12:21.139
I told D, I said, "Well, all the comments don't go over there."So comment something nice on the new one when this thing goes public.

02:12:21.140 --> 02:12:24.672
Yes, on the video. On the video, it helps us with the algorithm.

02:12:24.673 --> 02:12:33.353
That's why I asked you. You know, we hit a thousand subscribers in Germany today. Is that so cool?

02:12:33.354 --> 02:12:38.403
I was like, "Look, we got a thousand people."I told Braden, I said, "We're like apostles.

02:12:38.404 --> 02:12:42.215
We have churches all over the place. We got a church in Germany.

02:12:42.216 --> 02:12:50.866
We got a church in Japan. We got a church in South Korea. We got a church in, I don't know, Vietnam.

02:12:50.867 --> 02:12:59.723
We got one in the Philippines. We got one in France. Look at us."I didn't realize that my son—we have over ten in Russia.

02:12:59.724 --> 02:13:09.731
We have over ten channels now. Ten channels for ten churches, ten praying churches, all to the glory of God.

02:13:09.733 --> 02:13:15.514
Is that amazing? Ten churches, ladies and gentlemen, is what we have now, is what we call them.

02:13:15.515 --> 02:13:19.359
They're not subscribers and channels; these are churches.

02:13:19.360 --> 02:13:27.056
So, we have ten churches throughout America—I mean, around the world—that are watching us and getting these videos.

02:13:27.057 --> 02:13:36.652
So, Braden has a lot of work to do. We do these lives because he doesn't have to edit and do all the things he does, so he can just upload.

02:13:36.653 --> 02:13:43.358
It saves him a lot of time when we do lives. Do you like praying with us live every day? I could do more prayer lives.

