02:14:01.546 --> 02:14:11.831
I mean, tonight we got here and now it's after. So, we've been here a long time, but I felt a lot.

02:14:11.832 --> 02:14:18.368
Over this month, I've been praying over it. So if you like it, support it and I'll keep doing it.

